  }, "We've seen an example of structural drift (e.g., schema change); this occured when the gender column was updated. The example of hospitalization_days, where the value changes from estimated to actual demonstrates semantic drift\u2013the meaning of the data has changed but the structure (i.e., schema) hasn't.")), mdx("p", null, "In benign instances, model performance degrades and CTR drops a bit. It\u2019s far more damaging if it leads to a loss in ", mdx("a", {
